So:

key = "opst"

Step 3Ô∏è‚É£ Store in dictionary
groups = {
    "opst": ["pots"]
}

Step 4Ô∏è‚É£ Next word "tops"
key = "opst"
groups["opst"].append("tops")


Now:

"opst": ["pots", "tops"]

Final Dictionary
{
  "act": ["act", "cat"],
  "opst": ["pots", "tops", "stop"],
  "aht": ["hat"]
}

